f Feeding_Dino_004.png", "id": "1995034920942113", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974778_1995034924275446_680223155151981990_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DqU3YB_4gUkQ7kNvgFfsydX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAB-KclpSxAoSD9_iEJiKtnOQ0Dbc9tA4IPzEow1npbDw&oe=67825813"}, {"file_name": "Scanning_Tree_003.png", "id": "3871090536500485", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982458_3871090539833818_2097120813166486758_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5MBmQGVycfgQ7kNvgH0j0QD&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDSC6CGqic2Dnw9re46RF7Was-mE0_hw02LfCPCwxMOaQ&oe=67825F42"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Dino Hab - Landscape.png", "id": "551004384182173", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75221322_551004387515506_2539147473103521138_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rS2NQmhkXvsQ7kNvgGMlZsR&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDZj4sNfv1xAdKCBVfqMqpM3dCom0sbVcQhPd8q0b5znQ&oe=67827202"}, "display_name": "Dino Hab", "keywords": ["Dinosaur", "Simulation", "Cozy", "Strategy", "Travel"], "long_description": "# Catastrophe has struck the prehistoric world in this ecosystem simulation game.\n\nAs a new cadet of the time-traveling Paleoguard, it\u2019s up to you to restore prehistoric habitats and nurture baby dinosaurs into powerful adults with thriving herds.\n\n**Nurture Your Dinosaurs**\n\nRaise baby dinosaurs from hatchlings to towering adults. Bond with them as you care for their needs and watch your herds grow over time.\n{568429965856480}\n\n**Manage Your Habitats**\n\nDiscover and build unique evolving habitats for your dinosaurs with a variety of plants and fungi, while adapting to challenges like storms and volcanic eruptions.\n\n{340537239147832}\n\n**Unlock Rewards and New Ecosystems**\n\nYour progress will earn you rewards and unlock new habitats. 3 full habitats are included with their own dinosaurs, climate, flora, fauna, fungi, and more.\n{1954003895109712}\n\n\n**Your Personal AI Companion**\n\nYour AI companion, Puck, will travel with you between present day in mixed reality, to the virtual prehistoric world. Call on puck for support as you restore balance to the prehistoric ecosystems.\n\n{1098180671877626}\n", "short_description": "Catastrophe has struck the prehistoric world in this ecosystem simulation game. As a new cadet of the time-traveling  Paleoguard, it\u2019s up to you to restore prehistoric habitats and nurture baby dinosaurs into powerful adults with thriving herds.\n\nExplore and build evolving habitats for your dinosaurs, while overcoming environmental challenges like storms and volcanic eruptions. The more you bond with and care for your dinosaurs, the more rewards and new ecosystems you\u2019ll unlock.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.dinohab.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "30 Ninjas", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://dinohab.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}, {"id": "1725996564472128"}, {"id": "1043107547362485"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "SITTING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8583469981740789"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 6, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2253239078391256"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "i